# vCard 3.0 (RFC 2426 §3.1) mandates CRLF line endings. Without this
# rule git's autocrlf normalises the CRLF the renderer emits back to LF
# on checkout (incl. CI runners), silently dropping the spec-compliance
# fix and breaking Apple's QR vCard parser (which is stricter than the
# Contacts.app file-import parser). Treat as binary so the byte content
# is preserved exactly on every machine.
*.vcf binary
